@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@username = admin
@password = 123456
@wrongPassword = wrong_password

### 正常路径：登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：获取当前登录用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### 正常路径：登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：登出后再次获取当前登录用户，预期 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### 异常路径：错误密码登录，预期 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{wrongPassword}}"
}

### 异常路径：缺少 password 字段，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}"
}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
  }
]
